      <title>亚马逊在最新一轮裁员中削减了数十个公司职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/amazon-cuts-dozens-of-corporate-jobs-in-latest-round-of-layoffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司 (Amazon.com Inc.) 正在裁减其通讯部门的数十名员工，这是该公司高管为削减成本和减少官僚主义而采取的最新一次裁员行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/amazon-cuts-dozens-of-corporate-jobs-in-latest-round-of-layoffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 19:32:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普官员讨论加强对英伟达中国销售的限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-officials-discuss-tightening-curbs-on-nvidia-china-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，特朗普政府官员正在探索对英伟达公司向中国出售芯片采取更多限制措施。他们强调，谈判还处于非常早期的阶段，新团队正在研究政策优先事项。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-officials-discuss-tightening-curbs-on-nvidia-china-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 18:01:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
